O

Open() - Constructor for class EReaderView.Open
Opens a book either by importing it or accessing it through the existing library.
Open(String) - Constructor for class EReaderView.Open
Modified version of Open() constructor, operating on the idea that the book already exists as a MenuItem and simply needs to be displayed from the library.
openBook() - Method in class Book
This method opens the current book to the either the first page in the book or whatever the current book marked page is.
openBook(String) - Method in class EReaderController
This method is used by the controller to interact with the library/model and the library's current displayed book to turn the current displayed book's to the first page.
openBook(String) - Method in class EReaderModel
This method is used to interact with the current displayed book in the library and turn its current page to the first one.
openFile(String) - Method in class EReaderController
This method is used by the controller to interact with the model and open a file in the library/model and set the file as book in the library.
